課程概述 Course Description
 

課程學習目標 Course Objectives
瞭解轉譯醫學之概念與重要性。 學習研究者如何從臨床疾病角度提出問題，設計實驗進行探討之相關知識 培養如何將研究理論轉譯而實際應用於臨床疾病治療之專業能力。 

課程進度 Course Outline


週次 Week進度說明 Progress Description
1Introduction2Toward the treatment for Noonan syndrome3國定假日4Drug repurposing for personalized medicine5Current research projects of the iWRR for novel therapies of tissue 									 renegeration.6Pharmacogenetic Research and Clinical Implications in Colorectal Cancer7Development of RNAi eyedrop to treat myopia8My Translation Medicine Researches on Cardiovascular Disorders9Pancreas transplantation.10Translational research of modulation of DNA repair enzyme, O6-methylguanine 						methyltransferase in human cancers11My career development and pathway through small science12The significance of tumor associated macrophages in cancer.13Mechanobiology of cancer and organ failure.14From primary immunodeficiency to redox regulation.15Identification of breast cancer stem cells biosignature and targeting strategies.16Rab37, a vesicle trafficking mediator as a tumor suppressor in lung cancer.17Using endogenous protective pathways to combat neurodegenerative disease.18期末報告 

